title: DDFP 371: Who wins the AFC North?
itunes:title: DDFP 371: Who wins the AFC North?
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank and NFL.com Fantasy writer Alex Gelhar to discuss Adrian Peterson's restructured contract (11:19) plus Dez Bryant's and Demaryius Thomas' new deals (22:45). The guys then list what each team in the AFC North needs to do in order to win the division (27:32). Lastly, "Dead or Alive" makes a return (45:20).
